humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: The pathology report does not provide information on the number of positive lymph nodes or any metastases in the lymph nodes. Based on the new rules 10 and 11, N0 can indicate no metastatic carcinoma in sentinel lymph nodes and regional lymph nodes or that all assessed lymph nodes are negative for metastatic carcinoma. Therefore, the N stage for this patient is N0.

humanMachineDialogue.author: ZS Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: The report does not mention any involvement of regional lymph nodes (NOS), which means that there is no evidence of regional lymph node metastasis. Therefore, the pathologic N stage for this patient's cancer is N0.
